I like this board. Its dressed up real nice but not too many people know much about nuclear power. I doubt many would have anything to say. Make some more user friendly topics. Not nuclear related.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub97.ezboard.com/uprojectorion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>projectorion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Nuclear Renaissance Man</span><br>  Posts: 855<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(4/2/02 3:04:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=35.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~nuclearspace/ezboard/images/posticons/1.gif" align=absmiddle>  Combing cats.</span><hr size=1> I never comb my cat. Did you mean combining categories? I think you're right. More than I was. We just need some more space categories. I'm sure we can think of a few. Astronomy should definately be one.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub97.ezboard.com/uprojectorion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>projectorion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Nuclear Renaissance Man</span><br>  Posts: 875<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(4/3/02 5:47:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=35.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.fas.org/nuke/hew/Usa/Tests/Rwmohawk2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~nuclearspace/ezboard/images/posticons/Bart-term.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: More Space.</span><hr size=1> Asteroid Watch.<br>
